      *---------------------------------------------------------------------
      * {FILE_TYPE}: {FILE_NAME}
      * Description: {DESCRIPTION}
      * Author: {AUTHOR}
      * Created: {DATE}
      *---------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Purpose: {PURPOSE}
      *   - {PURPOSE_ITEM_1}
      *   - {PURPOSE_ITEM_2}
      *   - {PURPOSE_ITEM_3}
      *
      * Features:
      *   - {FEATURE_1}
      *   - {FEATURE_2}
      *   - {FEATURE_3}
      *
      * Usage: {USAGE_EXAMPLE}
      *
      * Record Formats:
      *   - {RECORD_FORMAT_1}: {RECORD_FORMAT_1_DESC}
      *   - {RECORD_FORMAT_2}: {RECORD_FORMAT_2_DESC}
      *
      * Key Fields:
      *   - {KEY_FIELD_1}
      *   - {KEY_FIELD_2}
      *
      * Reference:
      *   {REFERENCE_URL}
      *
      * Modification History:
      *   {VERSION} {DATE} | {AUTHOR} | {CHANGE_DESCRIPTION}
      *---------------------------------------------------------------------
     A          R {record_format}           PFILE({physical_file})
      *
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      * Field Selection (if needed)
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
     A            {field_name1}
     A            {field_name2}
     A            {field_name3}
      *
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      * Select/Omit Criteria (if needed)
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
     A          S {field_name}              COMP(EQ '{value}')
      *   or
      *         O {field_name}              COMP(EQ '{value}')
      *
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      * Key Specification
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
     A          K {key_field1}
     A          K {key_field2}
      *
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      * Join Logical File Example (if needed)
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      *         R {record_format}           JFILE({file1} {file2})
      *         J                           JOIN({file1} {file2})
      *         J                           JFLD({join_field1} {join_field2})
      *
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      * Fields from File 1
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      *           {field_name1}              JREF({file1})
      *
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      * Fields from File 2
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      *           {field_name2}              JREF({file2})
      *
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      * Key Specification for Join
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      *         K {key_field}
      *
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
      * End of Logical File
      * ----------------------------------------------------------------
